{"tid":1783392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個月合法抗爭試驗計劃","createTime":"2019-12-14T18:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T03:16:42.000Z","uid":287840,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"19acb7719910d0c16cebd07d8a499247eb37d8d5","tid":1783392,"uid":287840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:07:49.000Z","msg":"自從理大一役之後，<br />\n無論你幾唔想承認都好，<br />\n勇武真係少左好多，<br />\n成6000個手足俾人拉左，<br />\n對場運動影響好大，<br />\n黎明行動已經唔夠人搞...<br />\n<br />\n咁我地之後條路應該點行？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人有兩個弱點，就係太善良同鐘意番工。與其去勉強香港人做唔擅長既野，不如用香港人既方式去抗爭！撤撤底底咁做！唔係淨係做一兩日！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n罷工係香港咁激烈既經濟環境之下，大家都知其實好難搞得成......但係都要照搞！所以係工會籌備期間，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地依家只可以依靠和理非既方法全面抗爭，唔可以再靠街頭戰去分擔！以前係50比50，依家要做到90(和理非)比10(勇武)！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣照做，聖誕更加要和你shop<br />\n<br />\n1月to do list:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1）每人！每一日！都只可以幫襯黃店，中間綠色冇表態都唔好幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n2)所有星期六係港島，最好尖沙咀，搞完全和理非大遊行(要申請不反)，都係唔裝修唔搞黨鐵住唔佔路！只用人數make noise ，兼趕走大陸遊客。<br />\n<br />\n3)所有星期日搞10區和理shop,我講緊既係裝修都唔裝，只係靠人數逼爆商場，咁班死狗就冇理由拉人，因為我地冇犯法！<br />\n<br />\n4)除左必需品，盡量零消費！真係想買野可以考慮去外國網網購。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解要試驗？唔係應該長期做咩？因為，好多和理非做得唔夠徹底，成效唔夠大！我想俾所有和理非知，其實大家可以做到好多野，而且做緊既野係有效有用！勿以善小而不為！</span></span></strong>見到成效之後我地就要keep住做，直到香港經濟頂唔住！<br />\n<br />\n同埋最緊要唔送頭，班狗冇理由搞我地，就算鳩拉人都唔撚吿得入，因為我地冇犯法！<br />\n<br />\n試下做一個月，睇下當大家都岀盡全力all in會點，到時就會知和理非可以達到既最大效用去到邊！6000個手足將希望放囇落我地到，一齊試下好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e430a5395e0a292dd989182a11e5cb558de1f3","tid":1783392,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推，今日既行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a77EG51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa77EG51.jpg&h=a86f9171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7yo8L2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7yo8L2.jpg&h=242df1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmC9jSP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmC9jSP.jpg&h=8bedeaeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e38ce018fba90373784a977912814e94f1c943a","tid":1783392,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:11:56.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6d5ad8295e47c8176b6849063a82194c1c919f72","tid":1783392,"uid":85681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:14:34.000Z","msg":"值得試！推"},{"pid":"9a73f6400122c545b6bfc24ea3976cdf778f8f5e","tid":1783392,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推一推 可以試下！"},{"pid":"b19f3bb1953b24e070649170094cfbc1d5884c17","tid":1783392,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:15:32.000Z","msg":"ching 唔係想話咩 但想講半夜三更 咁多紅字放到咁大 睇得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完眼都盲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望大家少啲 size5紅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6204ab22614891b3af3d5f0177f07293d940f2d","tid":1783392,"uid":71458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:23:58.000Z","msg":"有意思 推<br />\n可能要一百個和理非先出到一個勇武嘅影響力